06:26.000 --> 06:28.000
Unlike in Taiwan, Japan, Germany,

06:28.000 --> 06:30.000
the United Kingdom, or France,

06:30.000 --> 06:32.000
we can choose the law department

06:32.000 --> 06:34.000
after graduating from high school.

06:34.000 --> 06:36.000
After graduating from the law department,

06:36.000 --> 06:38.000
