08:41.000 --> 08:43.000
What you teach is to teach some legal writing,

08:43.000 --> 08:45.000
mathematical writing, and so on.

08:45.000 --> 08:47.000
These are related to food.

08:47.000 --> 08:48.000
During the three years you teach,

08:48.000 --> 08:51.000
