12:35.000 --> 12:41.000
It means that

12:41.000 --> 12:43.000
if you are not in the U.S. today,

12:43.000 --> 12:45.000
for example, the U.K., France,

12:45.000 --> 12:47.000
Taiwan, or Japan,

12:47.000 --> 12:49.000
you have already studied law in college.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.000
So it is an abbreviation

12:51.000 --> 12:53.000
for a legal master's degree

12:53.000 --> 12:55.000
for foreigners.

12:55.000 --> 12:57.000
This is called LLM.

12:57.000 --> 13:00.000
You only need to study for nine months

13:00.000 --> 13:02.000
