At least on the surface,

49:29.000 --> 49:31.000
when you talk about

49:31.000 --> 49:33.000
multilateralism,

49:33.000 --> 49:35.000
it feels like you're talking about

49:35.000 --> 49:37.000
a country with different laws

49:37.000 --> 49:39.000
