56:13.000 --> 56:15.000
At the same time,

56:15.000 --> 56:17.000
the diplomat is not civilized at all.

56:17.000 --> 56:19.000
The diplomat is more like

56:19.000 --> 56:21.000
a governor-general,

56:21.000 --> 56:23.000
or even more like

56:23.000 --> 56:25.000
a magistrate in China,

56:25.000 --> 56:27.000
like Bao Qingtian,

56:27.000 --> 56:29.000
who is both a mayor and a judge.

56:29.000 --> 56:31.000
Furthermore,

56:31.000 --> 56:33.000
the U.S. was not a rich country

56:33.000 --> 56:35.000
at that time.

56:35.000 --> 56:37.000
The U.S. did not invest

56:37.000 --> 56:39.000
a lot of personnel,

56:39.000 --> 56:41.000
finance,

56:41.000 --> 56:43.000
and legal professionals in China.

56:43.000 --> 56:45.000
For example,

56:45.000 --> 56:47.000
the U.S. sentenced a person to prison.

56:47.000 --> 56:49.000
At first,

56:49.000 --> 56:51.000
the U.S. did not even have a prison.

56:51.000 --> 56:53.000
The U.S. even rented a prison

56:53.000 --> 56:55.000
to the British and French,

56:55.000 --> 56:57.000
because the U.S. built a prison

56:57.000 --> 56:59.000
in Shanghai earlier than the French.

56:59.000 --> 57:01.000
Why did the U.S. have

57:01.000 --> 57:03.000
