59:47.000 --> 59:49.000
The frequency of

59:49.000 --> 59:51.000
extraterritoriality

59:51.000 --> 59:53.000
and consular jurisdiction

59:53.000 --> 59:55.000
increased significantly

59:55.000 --> 59:57.000
after 1900.

